title: Large 2 Bed/1 Bath Apt By Owner For Rent Jackson Heights/East Elmhurst
posting_body: ['We are renting two bedroom, 1 bath apartment on the second floor of 2 family house.', 'It has one large living room, 2 bedrooms, kitchen with dishwasher and dining space.', 'It is in excellent condition.', 'It is good for a family/ professional people.', 'Living room has surround music system for music lovers.', 'It is available starting August 1st.', 'It is close to shopping area, bullova office and bus service.', 'There is a bus stop at a walking distance which takes you to the 74th Street Jackson Heights subway in 7 minutes.', 'It is close to Home Depot, Bed Bath and Beyond.', 'Rent includes everything, you need to pay for cooking gas and electricity.', 'Driveway is also available for extra $200 per month.', 'You can call me(Anil), prefer text', 'We need rent for first month, last month and the security deposit.', 'We would verify your information.']
